<!-- ── WHY SUSTAINABLE TOURISM MATTERS ────────────────────── -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="sec-hd center fade">
      <span class="sec-label">Why It Matters</span>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Sustainable Tourism<br>Is the Future</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p class="sec-sub">Climate change is reshaping tourism. Businesses that adapt with sustainability-first practices will lead — those that don't will be left behind.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-row">
      <div class="gc fade d1">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 14.76V3.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0v11.26a4.5 4.5 0 1 0 5 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Climate Risk Is Real</div>
        <p class="c-text">Tourism sites worldwide face rising sea levels, extreme weather, and ecological degradation. Proactive climate planning is essential for survival and long-term profitability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gc fade d2">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6 2 2 8 2 14c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8 1.4 0 2.8-.4 4-1 4-2 6-6.4 6-10C20 5.6 16.4 2 12 2z"/><path d="M2 14c4-2 8-2 12 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Eco-Travelers Demand More</div>
        <p class="c-text">Over 73% of global travelers now prioritize eco-certified destinations. Sustainability is a competitive advantage that directly impacts bookings and revenue growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gc fade d3">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Regulations Are Tightening</div>
        <p class="c-text">ESG compliance, carbon reporting, and environmental standards are rapidly becoming legal requirements for tourism operators across the Philippines and globally.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

